This is a clone of tetris, I created this for a class project.
Im mostly uploading this as a way to learn how to use git so dont take this to seriously.


The controls can be edited at the top of main.py

Controls (default):

Up Arrow - Rotate
Down Arrow - lower piece
Left/Right Arrow - left and right
Escape - pause/unpause
Right ctrl - hold piece

Controls (wasd):

W - Rotate
S - lower piece
A/D - left and right
Escape - pause/unpause
Left ctrl - hold piece
